citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:57 PM on
18-Oct-16.
The inspector knocked at the front door of the residence and then called the phone number provided. The inspector
also waited at the property for 30 minutes.
